data.description: Seller offering up to $10K in non-recurring closing costs. Welcome home to this perfect sized 3 Bedroom, 2 Bath Home with a Study/Office in Manor's desirable Shadowglen neighborhood. Nestled in the sought-after community of Shadowglen, this home offers a perfect blend of modern comfort and classic elegance, creating an inviting space. Open-concept living areas showcase abundant natural light and a seamless flow, perfect for entertaining guests or simply enjoying quality time. Create your personal oasis in the oversized backyard, or just relax on the covered patio. The opportunities to create the perfect first time or forever home are truly endless. Situated in a prime location, this property offers easy access to a plethora of amenities. Enjoy a round of golf at the nearby Shadowglen Golf Club, take a refreshing dip in the community pool, or explore the nearby parks and nature trails. The neighborhood is also within proximity to schools, shopping centers, dining establishments, and major commuter routes (290/130/183), making daily living a breeze. New Roof installed in June 2023.
